[section#exec.snd.general
    [:en] General
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] Subclauses [#exec.factories] and [#exec.adapt] define
customizable algorithms that return senders.
[:zh_CN] 子条款 [#exec.factories] 和 [#exec.adapt] 定义了返回发送器的可定制算法。

[:en] Each algorithm has a default implementation.
[:zh_CN] 每个算法都有缺省实现。

[:en] Let [`sndr] be the result of an invocation of such an algorithm or an object
equal to the result ([#concepts.equality]), and let [`Sndr] be [`decltype((sndr))].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`sndr] 为调用这种算法的结果或者等于这种结果的对象（[#concepts.equality]），
并令 [`Sndr] 为 [`decltype((sndr))]。

[:en] Let [`rcvr] be a receiver of type [`Rcvr] with associated environment
[`env] of type [`Env] such that [`[*:c sender-to]<Sndr, Rcvr>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`rcvr] 为 [`Rcvr] 类型的接收器，带有 [`Env] 类型的关联环境 [`env]，
使得 [`[*:c sender-to]<Sndr, Rcvr>] 为 [`true]。

[:en] For the default implementation of the algorithm that produced [`sndr],
connecting [`sndr] to [`rcvr] and starting the resulting operation state ([#exec.async.ops])
necessarily results in the potential evaluation ([#basic.def.odr]) of a set of
completion operations whose first argument is a subexpression equal to [`rcvr].
[:zh_CN] 对于产生 [`sndr] 的算法的缺省实现，连接 [`sndr] 到 [`rcvr] 并启动所得的
操作状态（[#exec.async.ops]）必然导致潜在求值（[#basic.def.odr]）一组完成操作，
其第一个实参是等于 [`rcvr] 的子表达式。

[para]
[:en] Let [`Sigs] be a pack of completion signatures corresponding to
this set of completion operations, and let [`CS] be the type of the expression
[`get_completion_signatures<Sndr, Env>()].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`Sigs] 为对应于这个完成操作集合的完成签名的包组，并令 [`CS] 为表达式
[`get_completion_signatures<Sndr, Env>()] 的类型。

[:en] Then [`CS] is a specialization of the class template [`completion_signatures]
([#exec.cmplsig]), the set of whose template arguments is [`Sigs].
[:zh_CN] 则 [`CS] 是类模板 [`completion_signatures]（[#exec.util.cmplsig]）的特例，
其模板实参的集合是 [`Sigs]。

[:en] If none of the types in [`Sigs] are dependent on the type [`Env], then the
expression [`get_completion_signatures<Sndr>()] is well-formed and its type is [`CS].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`Sigs] 中的类型都不依赖于类型 [`Env]，则表达式
[`get_completion_signatures<Sndr>()] 是良构的，其类型为 [`CS]。

[para]
[:en] Each completion operation can potentially be evaluated on one of several
different execution agents as determined by the semantics of the algorithm,
the environment of the receiver, and the completions of any child senders.
[:zh_CN] 每个完成操作都有可能根据算法的语义、接收器的环境以及任何子发送器的完成，
在几个不同的执行代理之一上求值。

[:en] For a completion tag [`T], let [$[`Ds]_{[`T]}] be a pack comprised of the
set of domain tags associated with the execution agents that could potentially
evaluate any of the operation's completions with tag [`T].
[:zh_CN] 对于完成标签 [`T]，令 [$[`Ds]_{[`T]}] 为一个包组，由与可能求值任何标签为 [`T]
的操作的完成相关联的执行代理的域标签集合组成。

[:en] If there are no potentially evaluated completion operations with tag type [`T],
then [`get_completion_domain<T>(get_env(sndr), env)] is ill-formed; otherwise,
it has type [`[*COMMON-DOMAIN]<[$[`Ds]_{[`T]}]...>] ([#exec.snd.expos]).
[:zh_CN] 如果没有标签类型为 [`T] 的潜在求值完成操作，则表达式
[`get_completion_domain<T>(get_env(sndr), env)] 是不良构的；否则，它的类型是
[`[*COMMON-DOMAIN]<[$[`Ds]_{[`T]}]...>]（[#exec.snd.expos]）。

[begin:example]
[:en] Let [`sndr2] be the sender [`then(sndr, fn)].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`sndr2] 为发送器 [`then(sndr, fn)]。

[:en] [`sndr2] has the same [`set_value] completion domain tag as [`sndr],
but if [`fn][=']s evaluation is potentially throwing,
[`sndr][=']s [`set_error] completion domain tag would be
the [*COMMON-DOMAIN] of [`sndr][=']s value and error completion domain tags,
in accordance with the semantics of the [`then] algorithm ([#exec.then]).
[:zh_CN] [`sndr2] 具有与 [`sndr] 相同的 [`set_value] 完成域标签，但如果 [`fn] 的
求值是潜在抛出的，则 [`sndr] 的 [`set_error] 完成域标签将是 [`sndr] 的值和错误完成域标签
的 [*COMMON-DOMAIN]，符合 [`then] 算法的语义（[#exec.then]）。
[end:example]

[para]
[:en] If [`sndr] can determine that all of its completion operations with tag [`T]
happen on execution agents associated with a particular scheduler [`sch]
(as determined by the semantics of the algorithm, the environment of the receiver,
and the completion schedulers of any child senders),
then [`get_completion_scheduler<T>(get_env(sndr), env)]
is well-formed and has the type and value of [`sch]; otherwise, it is ill-formed.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`sndr] 能够确定其所有标签为 [`T] 的完成操作都发生在与某个特定调度器 [`sch]
相关联的执行代理上（由算法的语义、接收器的环境以及任何子发送器的完成调度器确定），则表达式
[`get_completion_scheduler<T>(get_env(sndr), env)] 良构并具有 [`sch] 的类型和值；否则，它非良构。

[begin:example]
[:en] Let [`sndr2] be the sender from the example above.
[:zh_CN] 令 [`sndr2] 为上面示例中的发送器。

[:en] The [`set_value] completion scheduler of [`sndr2] is
the [`set_value] completion scheduler of [`sndr], if any.
[:zh_CN] [`sndr2] 的 [`set_value] 完成调度器是 [`sndr] 的 [`set_value] 完成调度器（如果有）。

[:en] But [`sndr2] can only report a [`set_error] completion scheduler
when invocations of [`fn] are not potentially throwing or
when [`sndr] has no [`set_error] completions.
[:zh_CN] 但是，只有当 [`fn] 的调用不是潜在抛出的或者当 [`sndr] 没有 [`set_error] 完成时，
[`sndr2] 才能报告 [`set_error] 完成调度器。

[:en] When [`fn] can throw, [`sndr2] could complete with [`set_error] either
by forwarding an error completion from [`sndr] or
by completing with the exception thrown by [`fn], which would happen on
an agent associated with [`sndr][=']s [`set_value] completion scheduler.
[:zh_CN] 当 [`fn] 可以抛出时，[`sndr2] 可以通过转发 [`sndr] 的错误完成或者通过 [`fn]
抛出的异常来完成 [`set_error]，这将发生在与 [`sndr] 的 [`set_value] 完成调度器相关联的代理上。
[end:example]

[para]
[:en] If a user-provided implementation of the algorithm that produced [`sndr]
is selected instead of the default:
[:zh_CN] 如果为产生 [`sndr] 的算法选择了用户提供实现而非缺省实现，那么：

[list]
[item]
[:en] Any completion signature that is in the set of types denoted by
[`completion_signatures_of_t<Sndr, Env>] and that is not part of [`Sigs] shall
correspond to error or stopped completion operations, unless otherwise specified.
[:zh_CN] 除非另有规定，否则任何处于 [`completion_signatures_of_t<Sndr, Env>] 所代表的
类型集合中，但不属于 [`Sigs] 的完成签名，都应当对应于错误或停止完成操作。

[item]
[:en] If none of the types in [`Sigs] are dependent on the type [`Env], then
[`completion_signatures_of_t<Sndr>] and [`completion_signatures_of_t<Sndr, Env>]
shall denote the same type.
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`Sigs] 中的类型都不依赖于类型 [`Env]，则 [`completion_signatures_of_t<Sndr>]
和 [`completion_signatures_of_t<Sndr, Env>] 应当代表同一类型。
[list:end]

[para]
[%@lib [^unspecified-exception]]
[:en] Various function templates in subclause [#exec.snd] can throw an exception
of type [*unspecified-exception].
[:zh_CN] 子条款 [#exec.snd] 中的各种函数模板可以抛出类型为 [*unspecified-exception] 的异常。

[:en] Each such exception object is of an unspecified type such that a [~handler]
of type [`exception] matches ([#except.handle]) the exception object
but a [~handler] of type [`dependent_sender_error] does not.
[:zh_CN] 每个这样的异常对象都具有未指定类型，使得类型为 [`exception] 的[~处理器]与
该异常对象匹配（[#except.handle]），但类型为 [`dependent_sender_error] 的 [~处理器] 不匹配。

[begin:note]
[:en] There is no requirement that two such exception objects have the same type.
[:zh_CN] 不要求两个这样的异常对象具有相同的类型。
[end:note]
